item.title: CVE-2023-2843|2024-10-10T19:37:32.883Z -- unknown -- multiparcels%20shipping%20for%20woocommerce
item.description: The MultiParcels Shipping For WooCommerce WordPress plugin before 1.14.15 does not properly sanitize and escape a parameter before using it in an SQL statement, which could allow any authenticated users, such as subscribers, to perform SQL Injection attacks.
